<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Denied - Favour Furniture</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            background: #f8f5f0; 
            color: #333; 
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .error-container { 
            background: white; 
            padding: 50px; 
            border-radius: 15px; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        .error-icon { 
            font-size: 80px; 
            color: #f39c12; 
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 { 
            color: #2c3e50; 
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 36px;
        }
        p { 
            color: #666; 
            margin-bottom: 25px; 
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .btn { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: #8B4513; 
            color: white; 
            padding: 12px 30px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 5px; 
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn:hover { 
            background: #A0522D; 
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #2c3e50;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #34495e;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-icon">â›”</div>
        <h1>403 - Access Denied</h1>
        <p>You don't have permission to access this resource. This area is restricted to administrators only.</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
            <a href="/" class="btn">Go to Homepage</a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-secondary">Login as Admin</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>